Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,若い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ バカが！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,ベル様っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-ヴァアー\N-さあーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,げえっ！
